Subject: [Blue Halo] Management Console is inaccessible after importing TLS cert
Description: Blue halo added their TLS certificate body and key into "Appliance > Server Maintenance > Server Certificate" yesterday afternoon. Since then, their management console has been inaccessible.
Solution_Comment__c: The key length was the issue, we had incorrectly set the RSA key to only 1024 bits when manually generating the key.
